Package: hurdlebb
Title: Hurdle Beta-Binomial Models for Bounded Discrete Proportions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("JoonHo", "Lee", , "jlee233@ua.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4019-8703"))
Description: Fits two-part hurdle beta-binomial models for bounded discrete
    proportions with structural zeros. Supports survey-weighted
    pseudo-posterior inference, state-varying coefficients, sandwich
    standard errors, and marginal effect decomposition via 'CmdStan'.
    Designed for analysis of complex survey data where a proportion of
    units report zero counts.
